snippet.title: Circle Of Sumo - Official Trailer 2018 [Nintendo Switch]
snippet.description:
Circle Of Sumo is available now on Nintendo Switch!

Up for a Local Multiplayer game? This is the Local Multiplayer game!
Circle Of Sumo will be out on Nintendo Switch on November 16, 2018!
- Up to 4 local players
- 8 different characters with different attributes
- 24 ridiculous sumo arenas
- 4 extra-games for extra fun
- 2 yummy single-player mini-games
